dct_title_s: Oil and gas fields of the state of Wyoming
dct_description_sm: compiled under the direction of G.B. Richardson and K.C. Heald ; oil and gas drafting by Lewis B. Pusey.
Includes "Index to locations of anticlinal axes" and diagram showing relation of the state to sheets of the International Map of the World at 1:1,000,000.
